data.description: Motivated Seller! Fantastic Rockwall ISD home in the highly sought-after Breezy Hill community of North Rockwall. This floorplan offers tons of potential with the 3 car garage, 2 first floor bedrooms, a true home office, and formal dining space. The second floor features a second living area, media room, 2 additional bedrooms, and a full bath. The heart of this home features an open-concept kitchen and living area with a custom paint scheme on the cabinets and island, gold-colored pulls, and high ceilings. This space is perfect for entertaining or unwinding after a long work day. Another significant aspect of this home is that you have a second bedroom on the first floor with a full bath, which is secluded from the rest of the house, making it perfect for an in-law suite, older child suite, or more. The community of Breezy Hill features a community pool, parks, and walking trails, all conveniently located in downtown Rockwall and all major shopping.
